<p class="ltx_p">This is to say, the function <math id="S0.I1.i2.p1.m2" class="ltx_Math" alttext="x\mapsto d(x,B)" display="inline"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>â†¦</mo><mrow><mi>d</mi><mo>â¢</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow></math> is <math id="S0.I1.i2.p1.m3" class="ltx_Math" alttext="1" display="inline"><mn>1</mn></math>-Lipschitz.</p>
</div>
<div class="ltx_proof">
<h6 class="ltx_title ltx_runin ltx_font_italic ltx_title_proof">Solution.</h6>
<div id="S0.I1.i2.p2" class="ltx_para">
<p class="ltx_p">To remove the infimum choose some <math id="S0.I1.i2.p2.m1" class="ltx_Math" alttext="\varepsilon&gt;0" display="inline"><mrow><mi>Îµ</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math>. Then we can choose
<math id="S0.I1.i2.p2.m2" class="ltx_Math" alttext="z\in B" display="inline"><mrow><mi>z</mi><mo>âˆˆ</mo><mi>B</mi></mrow></math> such that we are <math id="S0.I1.i2.p2.m3" class="ltx_Math" alttext="\varepsilon" display="inline"><mi>Îµ</mi></math>-close to the infimum</p>
<table id="S0.EGx3" class="ltx_equationgroup ltx_eqn_align ltx_eqn_table">

<tbody id="S0.Ex5"><tr class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_row ltx_align_baseline">
<td class="ltx_eqn_cell ltx_eqn_center_padleft"></td>
<td class="ltx_td ltx_align_right ltx_eqn_cell"><math id="S0.Ex5.m1" class="ltx_Math" alttext="\displaystyle d(y,z)\leq d(y,B)+\varepsilon\implies-d(y,B)\leq\varepsilon-d(y,%&#10;z)." display="inline"><mrow><mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mo>â¢</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>z</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>â‰¤</mo><mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mo>â¢</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>Îµ</mi></mrow><mo>âŸ¹</mo><mrow><mo>-</mo><mrow><mi>d</mi><mo>â¢</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow><mo>â‰¤</mo><mrow><mi>Îµ</mi><mo>-</mo><mrow><mi>d</mi><mo>â¢</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>z</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow></mrow><mo>.</mo></mrow></math></td>
