<p class="ltx_p">For <math id="S0.I1.i2.p2.m4" class="ltx_Math" alttext="z\in B" display="inline"><mrow><mi>z</mi><mo>âˆˆ</mo><mi>B</mi></mrow></math> we always have <math id="S0.I1.i2.p2.m5" class="ltx_Math" alttext="d(x,B)\leq d(x,z)" display="inline"><mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mo>â¢</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>â‰¤</mo><mrow><mi>d</mi><mo>â¢</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>z</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow></math>. Together this
results in</p>
