<p class="ltx_p">satisfies the following properties:</p>
<ul id="S0.I2" class="ltx_itemize">
<li id="S0.I2.i1" class="ltx_item" style="list-style-type:none;"><span class="ltx_tag ltx_tag_item">â€¢</span> 
<div id="S0.I2.i1.p1" class="ltx_para">
<p class="ltx_p"><math id="S0.I2.i1.p1.m1" class="ltx_Math" alttext="\forall x\in A" display="inline"><mrow><mrow><mo>âˆ€</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mo>âˆˆ</mo><mi>A</mi></mrow></math>, <math id="S0.I2.i1.p1.m2" class="ltx_Math" alttext="f_{A}^{\epsilon}(x)=1" display="inline"><mrow><mrow><msubsup><mi>f</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>Ïµ</mi></msubsup><mo>â¢</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></math></p>
</div>
<div class="ltx_proof">
<h6 class="ltx_title ltx_runin ltx_font_italic ltx_title_proof">Solution.</h6>
<div id="S0.I2.i1.p2" class="ltx_para">
<p class="ltx_p">For <math id="S0.I2.i1.p2.m1" class="ltx_Math" alttext="x\in A=\bar{A}" display="inline"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>âˆˆ</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mover accent="true"><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">Â¯</mo></mover></mrow></math> we have by <span class="ltx_ref ltx_ref_self"><span class="ltx_text ltx_ref_tag">1</span></span>
